# ENTITY::SET_PICKUP_COLLIDES_WITH_PROJECTILES

## Parameters
* **ENTITY_INDEX** entity
* **BOOL** collideWithProjectiles

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Sets whether a pickup will collide with projectiles.
